|''u-''||''m-''
|-
!3rd
|''a-''||''wa-''
|}
| &nbsp;&nbsp; ||
{| class=wikitable
|+ Object <br />prefixes
! Person ||Sg.||Pl.
|-
!1st
|''-ni-''||''-tu-''
